	LinkedSockets 6
	Rarity Normal
#-----------------------------------------
#	6-Socket Items
#-----------------------------------------
Show
	Sockets 6
	Rarity Normal
#-----------------------------------------
#	3-Color Items
#-----------------------------------------
Show
	SocketGroup RGB
	Rarity Normal
